Class CanonicalBusinessObjectReference

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.osate.ge.CanonicalBusinessObjectReference

  • public class CanonicalBusinessObjectReference
extends java.lang.Object
    Immutable data type for canonical references to a business object. A canonical reference uniquely identifies a business object.
